{"tid":234076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳橋工程檔案遭黑客加密勒索！路政署認3月初已知","createTime":"2017-05-08T03:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T06:15:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82c408c9fae3669d18a4c297b6b9e9b1be5ea8ed","tid":234076,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170508/large/1494212757_526d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170508%2Flarge%2F1494212757_526d.jpg&h=1b623e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路政署證實，港珠澳大橋一個地盤辦公室的電腦伺服器被勒索軟件攻擊，負責的工程公司已立即切斷伺服器的網絡連線，並向警方求助。該署指，被加密勒索的檔案中，不包括工人的個人資料，但該署並無交待被加密勒索的檔案有否涉及工程資料，只稱事件不影響工程進度。<br />\n<br />\n路政署表示，今年3月2日接獲港珠澳大橋粵港分界線至觀景山的香港接線駐工地工程人員通知，指辦公室內的伺服器被勒索軟件攻擊，伺服器內的部份檔案被加密勒索，工人已即時切斷伺服器的網絡連線，並向警方求助。被加密勒索的檔案中，不包括工人的個人資料。路政署已要求承建商更新辦公室內所有電腦的網絡保安軟件，有關事件並沒有影響工程進度。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，今次被黑客勒索軟件攻擊的相關工程公司是奧雅納工程顧問公司，該公司職員於3月2日發現在港珠澳大橋粵港分界線至觀景山的香港接線地盤的辦公室的電腦伺服器，遭黑客以加密勒索軟件攻擊，伺服器內多個檔案無法開啟，黑客要脅奧雅納付錢才可重新開啟檔案，職員立即切斷伺服器的網絡連線，並報警及向當局匯報事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56665065&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56665065%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170508&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQFKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=767e490a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56665065%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170508&h=1c7ebff3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56665065&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170508</a>"},{"pid":"9c280ea75d5dbc6a3fb8d14aa125fd1f458a5eba","tid":234076,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"ace8e7508e03caa6701fa697d2892574cddff0d7","tid":234076,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:40:44.000Z","msg":"上咩網先會中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d955d38e55ad3fb29543f5d08345707aae025038","tid":234076,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上咩網先會中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上咩網唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed256f5148a6db1c781f4bbf6a58c5d82a52e855","tid":234076,"uid":43760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上咩網"},{"pid":"97e71ce92a077d84754674403feca9eed5281a60","tid":234076,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b55e2e03f24258036cf20c9cd70a24452d50d7","tid":234076,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"又係外國勢力呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d837f1d068934e341c9eb036938e672267caa5e","tid":234076,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"ransomware，一定係d on9職員亂開d email attachment同click d link啦"}]}